com.seagate.csp.gui.view.prop

Interface TrayProperty

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTrayProperty, AnnotationTrayProperty, AttributesTrayProperty, AttributeTrayProperty, DateTrayProperty, ElapsedTrayProperty, EndTrayProperty, ErrorCodeTrayProperty, SbrTrayProperty, SerialNumberTrayProperty, SlotIndexTrayProperty, StartTrayProperty, StateTrayProperty, StatusTrayProperty, TestMessageTrayProperty, TestNameTrayProperty, TrayTrayProperty, TuidTrayProperty

    public interface TrayProperty
    Representation of a tray property. A property acts on a LocalTray. Each tray property has a name, a class possibly a comparator, and can change and be listened to. Tray properties have a native value, a string representation, a color representation and an icon representation.
